  "body": "Node stays out of sync, gossip blocks received frequently, number of peers is 25. I see a lot of logs like this:\r\n```\r\nIgnoring gossip block blockRoot=0x6ca67ba20f940f25e5d6        64af590b0f50f7537c9e204c25253ab6204cec8806d1, blockSlot=148684 code=BLOCK_ERROR_PARENT_UNKNOWN, parentRoot={}\r\n   5334 Error: BLOCK_ERROR_PARENT_UNKNOWN\r\n```\r\n\r\nIdeally the sync service should issue \"beacon_blocks_by_root\" request and node should be synced again, need to turn debug mode on to get more information.",
